चली बलखाती कहाँ रुक जा ओ पगली
नैनों वाली तेरे द्वार
लेके सपने हज़ार
जादू नगरी से आया है कोई जादूगर
लेके पहला पहला प्यार …

Absolute favorite ! Laxmikant-Pyarelal timeless magic, penned by Majrooh and best duet of Mukesh-Lata !
Honton Mein Aisi Baat
Abhi Na Jaa Mere Sathi :-)
Hum the jinke sahare, wo hue na humare ...

Ude jab jab zulfein teri...

Wishing A Very Happy Birthday To Dilip Kumar!
Tum mile to dil ke sare ghum gaye.

keh doon tujhse dil ke dukhde
ya aansoo pi jaoon
I dedicate this to All daughter and to all the lovely dads out there who love their princesses.
ke firr ye hasin raat ho na ho. hsyad fir is janam main mulakat ho na ho... Lag ja gale
Gayejaunga yehi geet main tere liye~~~~

Kuchh paa kar khona hai Kuchh kho kar paana hai
jeevan ka matlab to aana aur jaana hai
do pal ke jeevan se ek umra churani hai
zindagi aur kuchh bhi nahi teri meri kahani hai.
Dedicating this song to MY LOVE............
Mujhe tumse pyar tha, aaj bhi hai aur kal bhi rahega ..
Rula ke gaya sapna mera...
Main Koi Patthar Nahi Insan Hoon , Kaise Kah Doon Gam Se Ghabrata Nahi ...

Mera geet amar kar de..

message:
Na milti yeh bairan akhiyan 
chain na jaata dil bhi na rota
kaash kisi se pyar na hota~~~~~
Ek Sirf Humi Mai Ko ,Aankhon Se Pilate Hain , Kahne Ko To Dunia Mein ,Maikhane Hazaron Hain .....Wah !!
Aisa Sunder Sapna Apna Jeevan Hoga ...
Main Kaase Kahun Peer Apne Jia Ki Maai Ree ...
Wisdom of Words.....
Legendary Film Maker Yash Chopra passed away , may his soul rest in peace !
Guess friends , who's bithday we are celebrating today ? :) Jaldi karo :=)
One of the most inspirational song of Vinod Khanna ...!
Hello Friends........
I know I've made a lot of stupid mistakes. But the worst one was thinking the person who hurt me the most, wouldn't hurt me again.
hum to tere ashiq hai sadiyoo puranee....chahe tu mane chae na mane...!!!!!
Raah takte hain hum, jaane kis ke liye

Tere dar pe aaya hoon
kuch karke jaoonga...
Ek pal hai hansna ek pal hai rona kaisa hai jeevan ka khela -

Jo guzar rahi hai mujh per use kaise mein bataoon...
Wo khushi mili hai mujhko .. mein khushi se mar na jaoon...!!!

ツ
आज तक क़यामत है उसके लौट आने की उम्मीद,
आज तक ठहरी है जिंदगी अपनी जगह...
लाख ये चाहा की उसको भूल जाऊं,
हौंसले अपनी जगह बेबसी अपनी जगह...

 ツ
Tumne to dekha hoga usko sitaron ..aao zara mere sang mil ke pukaro ....!
zamana hai tumhara chahe jiski zindagi le lo, agar mera kaha maano aise khel na khelo .......Good Morning
Aankhon mein kisi ki wafa ka iqraar nahi milta .......! Milta hai kya ???

But if in your fear you would seek only love's peace and love's pleasure,
Then it is better for you that you cover your nakedness and pass out of love's threshing-floor,
Into the seasonless world where you shall laugh, but not all of your laughter, and weep, but not all of your tears.
Love gives naught but itself and takes naught but from itself.
Love possesses not nor would it be possessed;
For love is sufficient unto love. 
- Khalil Gibran

This song summarizes thought by Khalil Gibran in beautiful Urdu verses
Another gem of Gulzar ....!
Happy birthday to one of the finest lyricist Gulzar Saheb !!
Ka kare Yashoda Maiyya :=))

kaun saa ye bandhan hai?, ye kaisaa apnaapan hai ?
kisi kaa zor chale na, ye kaisi dil ki lagan hai

Remembering Rafi Sahab on his death anniversary and Mumtaz on her birthday. 

This song/movie had one of the best performances by both of them.
Doston ...Khoobsurat lyrics aur uske oper Mukesh ji aur Lata Di ki soft aur sweet unbeatable voice ....aapke liye ..chaliye sunte hain !!:=))
जिंदगी गुजारने को साथी एक चाहिये .... हुस्न गर नहीं ... शराब ही सही ... जब से वो गये हैं अपनी जिंदगी में एक नया दौर आ गया है ....

चाँद तनहा है आसमाँ तनहा ,
दिल मिला है कहाँ-कहाँ तनहा
YE KYA JAGE HAI DOSTO...........

Yeh , Kya Jagah hai Doston, Yeh Kaun sa dayaar Hai !
Hadeh Nigaah Tak Jahan, gubaar Hi Gubaar Hai !
